      <sec id="sec8">
        <title>Setting the dynamic sliding window bin</title>
        <p>This step refines the window bins to fit dynamic regions. We propose adopting a dynamic sliding window bin, distinct from existing methods. Based on candidate CNV and non-candidate CNV regions, we can set the different sizes of window bins. The size of the bin is dependent on the size of the region and can be calculated as:<disp-formula id="deqn07"><label>(9)</label><tex-math notation="LaTeX" id="DmEquation7">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
